      <entry><emphasis effect="italics">Initial dosage:</emphasis> 30 mg orally four times daily, before meals and at bedtime. Increase dosage gradually (given in divided doses three or four times daily) at one- to two-day intervals until optimum response is obtained.<newline/><emphasis effect="italics">Average optimum dosage:</emphasis> 180–360 mg daily.</entry>
