        <para id="para-00037">Ms. Tran follows up with her health care provider one week later to get the results of her diagnostic studies. The health care provider diagnoses her with hypertension stage 2 and starts her on enalapril, an ACE inhibitor. The nurse then teaches Ms. Tran about this new drug.</para>
